Author: psychedelic-sarah
Text: Where are you rn with your Ed or eating habits?? If you two are like totally not on the same page with eating, I’d say don’t message her but that’s just me, I feel like I’m not over my own issues so if I message someone or talk to someone who is so serious about recovery, it maKES ME WANNA RUN LIKE NOOOO but idk that’s me, but if you just wanna say hi or be nice and not be weird like me, you can shoot her a kind message :) (when I like ppls pics I don’t unlike them, I block them then unblock them, no fkn idea if that does jack shit but I do that literally every time lololol)
